<p>At first Dave and I were thinking flat spin, but in view of the chilly temps, we decided to climb and stay warm. Bow Mountain provided the right venue.</p>
<p>Indeed, we haven't been on its sandy switchbacks for some time. Though we didn't ride the "Roubaix" section, we did break a sweat on the tarmac.</p>
<p>On the way back, we waxed philosophical as is our custom. Great custom!</p>